y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83d130446e32182c57bbf6ed5610fd8abb1d140","tid":1980803,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"多謝台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間記者會仲有冇搞 可唔可以集合簽名去多謝佢哋"},{"pid":"d1d04762c24ccc3dfef70afd1add5ca3b0cd9275","tid":1980803,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ff9f6dc5b0d1351147c3351b44b20c36eca80f6","tid":1980803,"uid":244809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"留定言<br />\n遲下實有仆街係到鬥黃，又話人血饅頭，又話唔好食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"用「唔好食」做批鬥原因嘅人其實係想話俾世界聽佢仲係用個口諗嘢嘅中國人。"},{"pid":"a71f46ccbb136302cd6975e3145c036bebac2fbf","tid":1980803,"uid":35505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aegisvahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faegisvahk%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=2c0bda94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aegisvahk/</a><br />\n<br />\n快啲like保護傘個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8c275ac74db70cf27d4c552853823052b1e829","tid":1980803,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"台灣人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33b2eb2336c6901a8dcc7a42219473d86b082bb","tid":1980803,"uid":119126,"li