c=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f2c21a41389a486e7e327292e8f59eea21851c","tid":1980803,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35047831368ffd15841dba18bb76b60d8939ed8a","tid":1980803,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=abb228af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"81775ef0ea1543238d2c97234bc928c4b5349403","tid":1980803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a71f46ccbb136302cd6975e3145c036bebac2fbf","tid":1980803,"uid":35505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aegisvahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faegisvahk%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=2c0bda94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aegisvahk/</a><br />\n<br />\n快啲like保護傘個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"推 push"}]}